# UI motion (required)

Read `docs/UI_ANIMATIONS.md` before changing layout or navigation.

**Must port from v1** (`../misjuegos-master`):

1. Circular clip-path nav from hamburger origin (1000ms in / 500ms out)
2. Hamburger → X morph (0.2s)
3. Home FAB: main `-translate-y-full` + FAB 180° + plus 45° (1000ms)
4. List slide transitions; roulette springs; timer SVG sand; 3D dice (Phase 10)

**Brand:** dashed `border-4`, primary yellow on `#0f0e17`, Changa font. Avoid generic modal/nav patterns that replace these motions.

Phase 0 shell is simplified — Phase 3 completes animation parity.
